Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.93,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Esse anime não é recomendado para menores de 18 anos, e não é recomendado para pessoas sensíveis.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.93,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,{\pos(944,115.667)}Aviso a prova de frescos:
Dialogue: 10,0:00:05.97,0:00:07.65,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Aqui, Bell!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:10.85,0:00:12.39,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Essa doeu!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:12.39,0:00:14.82,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Você está bem, Bell?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:16.11,0:00:17.49,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Ai! Ai! Ai!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:19.30,0:00:22.58,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Bell, você não é muito... atleta, não é?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:23.12,0:00:25.96,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Cale a boca!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:26.71,0:01:29.80,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,As pessoas desse mundo\N estudam todo tipo de coisa.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:29.80,0:01:32.44,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Aprendi as normas com\N bastante facilidade, mas...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:32.44,0:01:34.89,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,A aula de ginástica também\N não é meu ponto forte.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:34.89,0:01:37.69,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,De qualquer forma, esportes como esse têm muito mais a ver com a memória muscular.{inclusive o nejeisu é mestre nisso em speedrun}
Dialogue: 10,0:01:37.69,0:01:39.66,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Bell, você está bem?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:40.06,0:01:41.90,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Hinata!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:41.90,0:01:45.65,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Por que tenho que jogar vôlei quando só quero sair contigo?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:45.65,0:01:46.83,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Ora, ora...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:46.83,0:01:50.18,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Fico feliz em ver que você\N está dando o seu melhor.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:50.18,0:01:52.92,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Sinto que você está se adaptando ao modo\N como as coisas funcionam por aqui.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:52.92,0:01:55.80,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Eu esperava que você me\N impressionasse ainda mais...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:57.34,0:01:58.92,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Tudo bem, então...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:58.92,0:02:00.13,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Bell?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.95,0:02:03.27,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Fique de olho em mim.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:03.27,0:02:04.79,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,S-Sim.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:18.60,0:02:20.39,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Ela está usando magia...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.39,0:02:23.25,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Mas acho que não há problema, desde que ela esteja se divertindo.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:20.39,0:02:22.10,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Acerte a bola, Sakura!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:22.10,0:02:23.25,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Consegui!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:30.00,0:02:30.96,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Bell! Você está bem?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.86,0:02:33.61,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Posso ser um pouco desajeitada.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.61,0:02:35.42,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Não é nada. Eu estou bem.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.42,0:02:37.67,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Não, você não está! Seu tornozelo\N precisa de tratamento!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:37.67,0:02:39.91,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Vamos levá-lo à sala da\N enfermaria. Vamos!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.91,0:02:42.17,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Tudo bem...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.92,0:02:46.25,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Mochida, informe o\N professor por mim.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:46.25,0:02:47.85,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Beleza.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.04,0:02:53.19,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Você está bem?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.04,0:02:53.19,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,{\fs75\pos(944,91)\fscx48\fscy52}Nota: o diálogo original o hinata fala "Daijoubu"  (大丈夫) que em pt-br é  "Você está bem?",  mas no script inglês oficial traduzido diz "É melhor assim?"  eu (nejeisu) decidi manter o original, pois o diálogo não perde e sentido nas linhas posteriores.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.19,0:02:56.35,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Sim, obrigado. Não está\N mais doendo.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.35,0:02:59.43,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Eu sinto muito. A culpa foi\N minha por pressioná-lo.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:59.43,0:03:00.97,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Isso não é\N verdade!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.97,0:03:04.41,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Na verdade, tenho sorte de poder passar algum tempo sozinho contigo.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.41,0:03:07.44,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Eu não gosto de ver\N você ferida, Bell...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.31,0:03:11.16,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Obrigado, Hinata.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.16,0:03:13.22,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Mas não se preocupe comigo.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.22,0:03:17.05,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Posso fazer tudo com\N você ao meu lado.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.05,0:03:19.83,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Nada me assusta quando\N você está por perto...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.83,0:03:22.03,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Então, fique comigo\N para sempre...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.03,0:03:24.28,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Não preste atenção a ninguém.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.28,0:03:26.06,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,{\k0}{\k49}Hi-{\k49}na{\k80}-ta...{\k0}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.06,0:03:27.59,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,S-Sim...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.59,0:03:28.50,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Ótimo!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:30.29,0:03:32.67,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Puxa, ela é forte...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:33.21,0:03:35.35,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Ah, eu sei! Use o feitiço mágico!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.35,0:03:36.65,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Qual feitiço?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:36.65,0:03:38.85,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Eu li sobre isso em\N um desses livros.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.85,0:03:41.76,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Ele dizia que você tem um feitiço mágico que faz a dor desaparecer.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.35,0:03:44.07,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,...Oh!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.07,0:03:47.02,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,"Dodóizinho, dodóizinho vá embora!”
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.07,0:03:47.02,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs60\fscx67\fscy81}Nota: eu adaptei essa parte pra "Dodóizinho, dodóizinho vá embora!” porque no inglês eles inventaram uma expressão inexistente e a minha adaptação é mais fiel ao japonês pois é uma tradução mais fiel de "Itai no" (痛い の) 
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.02,0:03:48.58,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Que tal?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.58,0:03:50.68,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Isso foi péssimo!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.68,0:03:52.47,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Fale como se estivesse\N realmente falando sério!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:52.47,0:03:54.76,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,O quê? Mas, uh...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.76,0:03:56.43,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Ah, coitado do\N meu pezinho!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.43,0:03:58.59,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Talvez eu nunca\N volte a andar!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.59,0:04:02.42,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Você terá que cuidar de mim pelo resto da minha vida ou então eu morrerei!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.04,0:04:05.05,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Tudo bem!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.71,0:04:08.52,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Então, vá em frente.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.63,0:04:14.96,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Que isso alivie a dor, mesmo que seja só um pouquinho...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.96,0:04:18.39,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,E que você nunca mais\N se machuque...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.76,0:04:22.69,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Não é suficiente. Mais.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.69,0:04:25.39,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,M-Mais? Beleza...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.11,0:04:34.08,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Bell, suas pernas... Elas são lindas...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:35.43,0:04:37.83,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Hinata, me beije aqui também...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.83,0:04:39.05,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,S-Sim...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.20,0:04:44.24,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Sua pele é tão macia...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.24,0:04:47.22,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Não quero que nenhum corte\N ou cicatriz o manche...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.49,0:04:50.43,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Você é a única pessoa que\N pode falar isso para mim...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.39,0:04:53.54,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Bell...!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:55.13,0:04:57.10,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Você não está usando um...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:57.10,0:04:58.21,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Não.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.21,0:04:59.43,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Muito desconfortável.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:59.43,0:05:01.86,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,E é para que você possa me\N tocar sempre que quiser.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:01.86,0:05:03.14,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,B-Bell?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.14,0:05:06.14,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Hinata... faça o feitiço no meu peito...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.47,0:05:10.61,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Bell, eu...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.08,0:05:15.54,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Desculpe-me! Eu o machuquei?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:15.54,0:05:16.88,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Tudo Bem...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.88,0:05:18.54,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Faça como quiser.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:18.54,0:05:20.40,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,B-Bell...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.87,0:05:29.28,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Bell, você está bem? Trouxe uma roupa para você.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.18,0:05:36.92,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Me desculpe por me intrometer!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:36.92,0:05:37.64,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Ei—!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.42,0:05:40.28,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Mochida-san, espere!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:40.28,0:05:41.87,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Mochida-san!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.98,0:05:46.68,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Quase o peguei...!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.16,0:05:54.12,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Desculpe-me por incomodá-lo em nosso dia de folga, Mochida-San.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.12,0:05:57.54,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Sem problemas. De todo modo, eu queria fazer compras.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.54,0:06:00.59,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Pensei que íamos\N sair juntos hoje...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:00.59,0:06:02.13,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Por que Sakura está aqui...?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.13,0:06:05.28,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Porque sou homem e não tenho\N experiência nessa área.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.28,0:06:09.91,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Para seu bem, achei que seria melhor que alguém com experiência nos acompanhasse.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.33,0:06:15.56,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Entendi. É a sua forma\N de cuidar de mim.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.56,0:06:17.00,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Então, está bem!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.00,0:06:21.53,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Nesse caso, não hesitarei em fazer compras até cair para você, Hinata!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:22.55,0:06:23.94,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,É tão grande...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.94,0:06:27.90,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Escolher roupas íntimas é algo que somente uma garota entenderia...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.94,0:06:25.93,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,{\an8)}O design é importante, sem dúvida.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.93,0:06:27.90,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Mas escolher o tamanho certo é fundamental.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.35,0:06:30.88,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Me dá só um minutinho, beleza?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.88,0:06:32.21,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,S-Sim.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.79,0:06:43.55,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Todas ficam ótimas em você!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.55,0:06:45.58,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,De que tipo você\N usa, Sakura?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.58,0:06:46.55,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Ahn?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:49.83,0:06:52.78,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Esse também é bonito.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.27,0:06:55.75,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Isso é vergonhoso...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.75,0:06:59.25,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Não há necessidade de ser tímido, já que somos meninas, certo?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.25,0:07:00.52,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Acho que sim...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.52,0:07:03.46,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Eu me pergunto se Sunohara prefere o grande ao pequeno...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:03.46,0:07:06.24,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Ah, já sei! Vamos pedir\N a opinião do Hinata!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:06.24,0:07:07.10,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Espere, Bell!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:07.10,0:07:08.49,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Dê uma olhada, Hinata!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.49,0:07:09.55,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Bell?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.55,0:07:11.69,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,O que você acha? Bonitinho, não é?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.69,0:07:14.48,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Você não pode sair pela loja com essa roupa!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:14.48,0:07:16.58,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Ah, você não gosta deste?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.58,0:07:18.98,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Certo, acho que vou escolher um diferente...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.12,0:07:23.30,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Bell! Volte para o provador!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.09,0:07:27.59,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Estou exausta.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.59,0:07:30.80,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Também estocamos vários\N itens essenciais.{ou nem tanto }
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.80,0:07:33.34,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Um passeio bem-sucedido! Você se divertiu?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.34,0:07:35.85,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,É claro.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.85,0:07:40.21,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Desculpe, preciso\N ir ao banheiro.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.21,0:07:42.42,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Não tenha pressa.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.79,0:07:47.26,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Ei, Bell? Posso lhe perguntar uma coisa?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.26,0:07:48.99,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,O quê?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.99,0:07:53.94,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Eu deveria ter perguntado antes, mas... você e Sunohara estão?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.94,0:07:55.58,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,O quê? Namorando?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.20,0:07:59.05,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Um casal, talvez?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.05,0:08:01.63,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Não, essa palavra também não é suficientemente forte...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:01.63,0:08:03.29,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Estou entendendo...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.29,0:08:04.92,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Por que você está\N perguntando?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.92,0:08:07.03,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Nada de especial, eu só estava curiosa! 
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.03,0:08:08.42,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Huh.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.42,0:08:13.03,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,De qualquer modo, Hinata e eu estávamos destinados um ao outro.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.03,0:08:14.63,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Você foi?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:15.24,0:08:20.39,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Hinata veio em meu socorro quando eu estava sendo atacado por humanos.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.39,0:08:23.71,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Até então, eu desprezava\N os humanos...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.92,0:08:28.41,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Mas... no momento em que coloquei os olhos em Hinata, eu soube.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.16,0:08:34.66,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,“Ah, o motivo pelo qual eu existo é para estar com essa pessoa.”
Dialogue: 10,0:08:35.99,0:08:38.99,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,E desde então, tenho me\N sentido da mesma forma.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.28,0:08:47.08,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Então, decidi que nunca mais\N sairia do lado de Hinata.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:47.08,0:08:51.91,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,É incrível a maneira como você não tem medo de dizer que o ama...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:52.41,0:08:54.62,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,É melhor eu melhorar o meu desempenho...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:54.62,0:08:56.24,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Você disse alguma coisa?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.24,0:08:58.83,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,N-N, Nada não!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.83,0:09:00.06,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Eu voltei.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.06,0:09:02.09,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Bem-vindo de\N volta, Hinata!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.09,0:09:02.92,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:02.92,0:09:05.42,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Mochida-san, tem\N algo errado?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.42,0:09:07.42,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Huh?! N-N,\N Nada não!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.49,0:09:16.72,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Devemos ir para casa?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.72,0:09:17.85,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Sim.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.04,0:09:20.91,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Mas antes...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.31,0:09:22.60,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Hinata?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.18,0:09:26.92,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Você se importa se fizermos\N um pequeno desvio?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:29.62,0:09:31.17,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,É lindo!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.17,0:09:33.87,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Eu não sabia que seu mundo\N tinha lugares como esse!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:33.87,0:09:37.45,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,E o campo tem ainda mais\N verde do que a cidade.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.45,0:09:39.67,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Mas por que você me\N trouxe até aqui?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:39.92,0:09:43.81,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,É que... Parecia que você precisava\N se animar um pouco.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:46.71,0:09:48.42,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Acho que você\N tem razão...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:48.42,0:09:53.03,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Eu me sinto mais em paz quando estou cercado pela natureza...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.03,0:09:54.51,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Sinto muito, Bell.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.51,0:09:57.64,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Perguntei muito a você sem levar em conta seus sentimentos...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.64,0:09:58.97,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Hinata?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.69,0:10:00.61,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Então...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.58,0:10:10.09,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Para compensar o dia de hoje,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.09,0:10:13.42,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Achei que poderíamos sair\N juntos agora, só nós dois.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.38,0:10:15.53,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Não é o suficiente...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:15.53,0:10:16.88,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.37,0:10:20.49,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Não é nem de longe é\N o suficiente, Hinata...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.49,0:10:23.09,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Preciso que preste mais\N atenção em mim.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.09,0:10:24.85,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Ignore todos os demais...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.85,0:10:28.17,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,E só eu terei olhos para você.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.17,0:10:29.59,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Por favor.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.05,0:10:44.15,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Finalmente encontramos!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.15,0:10:47.06,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Eu juro... Você não mudou\N nem um pouco, não é?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.06,0:10:47.87,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.80,0:10:52.16,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,É bom vê-lo novamente, Hinata-dono.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.16,0:10:53.51,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Yoo-hoo!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.51,0:10:55.53,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Cecil-san? Mei?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.53,0:10:56.92,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Mas por quê...?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.37,0:11:02.37,Century Gothic,,0,0,0,,Estamos aqui para trazê-la\N de volta ao lar, Mariabell.
